{"tid":478113,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)美帝特工 原子殺姬","createTime":"2017-11-23T17:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T20:31:03.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc90ca02e10b12acb6cca595487d649482547d8","tid":478113,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=jOq8K1o5peKA5FJpE7s9s54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5d3e4570\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=jOq8K1o5peKA5FJpE7s9s54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=cb0108e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/25/American_Assassin_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F25%2FAmerican_Assassin_Poster.jpg&h=1869b707&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://movie.yahoo-leisure.hk/assets/poster/AtomicBlond6021120832104019258_380x560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmovie.yahoo-leisure.hk%2Fassets%2Fposter%2FAtomicBlond6021120832104019258_380x560.jpg&h=b3bf6b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事敘述CIA探員米基&middot;拉普的女友因遭受恐怖襲擊而過世，使得米基陷入了極度哀傷。CIA副局長艾琳&middot;甘迺迪指派了史丹&middot;赫利來訓練米基，以幫助他走出悲傷並追捕恐怖主義的肇事者。他們一起調查了一波對軍方和平民的隨機攻擊，便為此與致命的土耳其探員共同行動，以阻止神秘人在中東展開世界大戰的陰謀<br />\n<br />\n2.冷戰時期，英國軍情六處的首席女特務露溫保杜(Lorraine Broughton)(查理絲花朗 飾)，向來無所不用其極完成不可能的任務，是MI6中最致命狠勁的間諜。她的最新任務是單人匹馬前往動蕩不安的柏林，追尋一份不翼而飛的間諜名單。露溫在柏林受四面埋伏，必須與情報探員大衛珀斯(David Percival)(占士麥艾禾 飾)合作，找出一線生機。這場諜戰危機足以威脅整個西方世界，第三次世界大戰一觸即發..<br />\n<br />\n1 20AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=jOq8K1o5peKA5FJpE7s9s54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b8ef087c\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=jOq8K1o5peKA5FJpE7s9s54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0ed672c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7933cd58e752f0087b583ab8b4a1f99a0425ec2f","tid":478113,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T17:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767e2e047f7d9a45bc281087f504415fc61a090e","tid":478113,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T17:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3023afaae869c65faa4c3e1670cf263478e6044e","tid":478113,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T18:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcf06ba7be411c6a